thread.title: Katherine Castillo
thread.title_full: Westminster Teak reviewed by Katherine Castillo

author: Katherine Castillo
title: Katherine Castillo
text: Excellent experience. Great chatting experience. Called to place my order and talked through all the choices. Chose the White Glove Delivery service and they were very flexible about postponing my delivery for a couple of weeks to accommodate my schedule. Love my table and chairs. Can't wait for my next purchase with this company.
